{"tid":2157987,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（戰敗75年）日本人參拜靖國神社  首相誓言不重複悲劇","createTime":"2020-08-15T12:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T14:01:43.000Z","uid":184679,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"419bf1445b6de443390d774980861ced17d4078f","tid":2157987,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T12:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/79C4B8B4-829A-4D6A-A137-F3BFE8EDEFDA_w408_r0_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2F79C4B8B4-829A-4D6A-A137-F3BFE8EDEFDA_w408_r0_s.jpg&h=2ae51e91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期六，成千上萬日本男女老少，在酷暑和新冠疫情中，參拜了東京有爭議的靖國神社（Yasukuni Shrine）。日本首相安倍晉三發表了紀念死者的講話，不過沒有親自前往參拜，以避免激怒中國和南​韓。<br />\n<br />\n日本首相安倍晉三在第二次世界大戰日本投降75週年紀念日上發表講話，誓言永不重複戰爭的悲劇；德仁天皇對至今仍然困擾著東亞的戰時歷史表示深深的懺悔。<br />\n<br />\n面戴口罩的安倍晉三說： &ldquo;永遠不要重複戰爭的悲劇。我們將繼續恪守這一堅定的承諾。&rdquo; 不過，他沒有像天皇一樣表示懺悔。<br />\n<br />\n南​韓總統文在寅與日本的關係因為歷史遺留問題而冷淡。他在講話中表示，首爾一直準備與東京討論歷史糾紛。<br />\n<br />\n至少有四名日本內閣大臣親自參拜了靖國神社，這裡供奉著14名戰犯和其他戰死者。<br />\n<br />\n北京和首爾把這座神社視為日本過去軍事侵略的象徵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/japanese-yasukuni/5544818.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fjapanese-yasukuni%2F5544818.html&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8fE18wtZo%2FyF0aYgy6X%2FhPY%3D&h=47d35aa7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/japanese-yasukuni/5544818.html</a>"},{"pid":"a223e1512b6984bf75c45cea0a5c215c3bcacbc5","tid":2157987,"uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T12:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i-lih-kg.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp1.pstatp.com%2Flarge%2Fcff0003aa8c7b137cf7.jpg&amp;h=a488d2ab&amp;s=540\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi-lih-kg.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fi.lih.kg%2Fthumbnail%3Fu%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fp1.pstatp.com%252Flarge%252Fcff0003aa8c7b137cf7.jpg%26h%3Da488d2ab%26s%3D540